property.name: Text
property.value: Hi traveluh! I'm Maahtin. Pleasure's mine, I'm sure. Now what brings you to our lovely island? Adventure? Plunder? Perhaps even... Rohmance? I assure you, you won't find a better place for ALL THREE than here, on Tottyhot. That's not the name of the place really it's just what I call it — I think it's better. Don't you agree? You do, you do, you're nodding, you do. Let me give you a piece of advice, traveluh: keep on your toes. You never know when you'll start having a real adventure! As for me — well, you didn't ask, but here's my story. I was abandoned by both my parents at a tender age, only about 29 or so. They told me to run, Martin, Run! There was a fire, I think? But nobody seemed to be getting hurt. Anyway I ran and then I never saw them again! They LEFT me. And so I left for my adventure, because that's what they would have wanted. My adventure led me here, to this island, where I found all the treasure I couldn't carry — friends. Family even! A new one. They gave me this entire room, can you believe it? I decorated it meself. Do you like it? Anyway, as I was saying, I found the plunder, the adventure, and the family, but never the rohmance. Have you ever looked for love, traveluh? Have you searched and searched and never found yourself in the throes of passion? In the depths of another's eyes? I can tell you that I haven't. My life story continues like this for pages and pages. But I'm boring you, aren't I? Am I? You can be honest with me...
